body_html: I have the same problem. Windows 10 64-bit, Python 3.6.6, Pip 18.0. Attempting to import it using "import tensorflow" in the interactive console results in all of the same errors as in the OP. Testing with Tensor-Self-Check gives the same log as the OP. TensorFlow 1.8 works fine, but both 1.9 and 1.10 give the error. I used coreinfo to check if my CPU supports AVX, and it does.
